articles.author: Ankur Banerjee
articles.title: Asian stocks hit 9-month lows on worries over China, US rates - Reuters
articles.description: Asian shares sank to nine-month lows on Thursday, while the dollar was at a two-month peak as fears over China's sluggish economic recovery and concerns that the Federal Reserve may still raise interest rates rattled investors.
